<your-username>.github.io/
├─ _config.yml                ← site settings & your social links/avatar path
├─ index.md                   ← HEADER (home page hero text)
├─ _data/
│  └─ navigation.yml          ← top navbar links (Projects, Certs, YouTube, Reach out)
├─ _pages/
│  ├─ projects.md             ← Projects section (your labs/repos)
│  ├─ certifications.md       ← Certifications section
│  ├─ youtube.md              ← YouTube section (video embeds)
│  └─ contact.md              ← “Reach out & connect” (LinkedIn/GitHub/Email)
└─ assets/
   └─ img/
      └─ profile.jpg          ← your profile picture file
